}}</ref></small>。

;史篤城
2009年1月12日比亞堤重返[[英超|英超]]，加盟[[斯托克城足球俱乐部|史篤城]]，轉會費沒有透露，但據報最終可達到350萬[[英鎊|英鎊]]，簽約兩年半<small><ref name="Striker Beattie signs for Potters">{{cite news
| title = Striker Beattie signs for Potters
| url = http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/s/stoke_city/7822688.stm
| publisher = [[BBC|BBC]] Sport
| date = 2009-01-12
| accessdate = 2009-01-12
| archive-date = 2020-05-11
| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200511133931/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/s/stoke_city/7822688.stm
| dead-url = no
}}</ref></small>，比亞堤上陣16場射入7球，協助球隊以第12位結束球季。但翌季比亞堤失去入球觸覺，上半季上陣19場僅在對[[西汉姆联足球俱乐部|韋斯咸]]射入兩球，自11月尾開始失去正選席位。12月5日史篤城作客0-2負於[[阿森纳足球俱乐部|阿仙奴]]，賽後比亞堤與領隊[[東尼·佩利斯|東尼·佩利斯]]在更衣室發生爭執<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/stoke_city/8399591.stm |title=Stoke investigate 'bust-up' between Pulis and Beattie |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2009-12-07 |accessdate=2010-08-16 |archive-date=2016-03-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160310122452/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/stoke_city/8399591.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，雖然球會向外宣稱兩人誤會平息，並拒絕[[英格蘭職業足球運動員協會|英格蘭職業足球運動員協會]]介入調解<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/stoke_city/8404916.stm |title=James Beattie row with Stoke is over, says PFA chief |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2009-12-09 |accessdate=2010-08-16 |archive-date=2016-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307123238/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/stoke_city/8404916.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，但自此比亞堤出場機會逐漸減少。有傳比亞堤會在1月[[轉會窗|轉會窗]]離隊，最終沒有成事，而比亞堤亦趁機於2010年3月為長期受傷患困擾的[[膝蓋|膝蓋]]進行[[手術|手術]]<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11095_6019160,00.html |title=Beattie out for six weeks |publisher=Sky Sports |date=2010-03-13 |accessdate=2010-08-16}}</ref></small>，於4月初復原並參與預備隊的賽事<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11095_6079811,00.html |title=Beattie back for season finale |publisher=Sky Sports |date=2010-04-07 |accessdate=2010-08-16 |archive-date=2016-03-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160310081443/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11095_6079811,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，於4月17日主場1-2負於[[博尔顿足球俱乐部|保頓]]在末段後補入替[[戴夫·傑臣|戴夫·傑臣]]<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/8617714.stm |title=Stoke 1-2 Bolton |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2010-04-17 |accessdate=2010-08-16 |archive-date=2020-08-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200811051210/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/8617714.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，是其效力史篤城最後一場賽事。

;格拉斯哥流浪
2010年8月13日比亞堤轉投[[蘇超|蘇超]]「[[老字號_(足球)|老字號]]」[[流浪者足球俱乐部|格拉斯哥流浪]]，轉會費沒有透露，簽約兩年，並可優先續約一年，是這支財困衛冕聯賽冠軍近兩年來首名買入的球員<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/r/rangers/8908183.stm |title=Rangers sign striker James Beattie from Stoke |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2010-08-13 |accessdate=2010-08-16 |archive-date=2020-05-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200526121753/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/r/rangers/8908183.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，取代離隊的[[克里斯·博伊德|-{zh-hans:克里斯·博伊德; zh-hk:基斯·保特;}-]]席位。但上半季僅取得10次上陣機會，沒有入球，於2011年1月31日被借用返回[[英格蘭|英格蘭]]效力[[黑池足球會|黑池]]直到球季結束<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/b/blackpool/9382499.stm |title=Andy Reid and James Beattie captured by Blackpool |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2011-01-31 |accessdate=2011-02-01 |archive-date=2011-03-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110325060540/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/b/blackpool/9382499.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2011年8月31日，比蒂和格拉斯哥流浪解约<ref>{{Cite news | url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/14742693.stm | title=Rangers release striker James Beattie | publisher=BBC Sport | date=1 September 2011 | accessdate=2011-09-04 | archive-date=2020-05-04 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200504223346/https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/14742693 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

;重返錫菲聯
2011年11月24日比亞堤重投剛季降班第三級[[英甲|英甲]]的舊東家[[谢菲尔德联足球俱乐部|錫菲聯]]，以短約形式效力至翌年1月中<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/15872372.stm |title=Striker James Beattie returns to Sheffield United |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2011-11-24 |accessdate=2011-11-25 |archive-date=2012-01-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120126230336/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/15872372.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。雖然備受傷患困擾及狀態低迷，他仍然獲得續約至球季結束<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.mirrorfootball.co.uk/news/James-Beattie-set-to-extend-barren-stay-with-Sheffield-United-article855891.html |title=Beattie set to extend barren stay with Sheffield United |publisher=''mirrorfootball.co.uk'' |date=2012-01-21 |accessdate=2012-11-10 |archive-date=2012-02-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120208125240/http://www.mirrorfootball.co.uk/news/James-Beattie-set-to-extend-barren-stay-with-Sheffield-United-article855891.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，但於季後被放棄<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/18264057 |title=Ched Evans among 11 players released by Sheffield United |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2012-05-30 |accessdate=2012-11-10 |archive-date=2015-01-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150106065021/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/18264057 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

;阿克寧頓
2012年11月9日比亞堤以自由身加盟由前[[布莱克本足球俱乐部|布力般流浪]]隊友[[尼廉·李察臣|尼廉·李察臣]]執教的[[英乙|英乙]]球會[[艾宁顿斯坦利足球俱乐部|阿克寧頓]]，擔任球員兼教練<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/20274301 |title=James Beattie becomes Accrington Stanley player-coach |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2012-11-09 |accessdate=2012-11-10 |archive-date=2016-01-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160108025642/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/20274301 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2013年5月13日比亞堤獲委為球隊新領隊接替離隊的[[尼廉·李察臣|尼廉·李察臣]]<ref>{{citenews |language=en |url=http://www.bbc.com/sport/0/football/22517827 |title=James Beattie is Accrington Stanley's new manager |work=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2013-05-13 |accessdate=2014-09-14 |archive-date=2015-09-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924192638/http://www.bbc.com/sport/0/football/22517827 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2014/15年球季於開季6戰僅得4分排名21位，執教16個月的比亞堤同意提前解約<ref>{{citenews |language=en |url=http://www.bbc.com/sport/0/football/29178841 |title=James Beattie: Accrington Stanley part company with boss |work=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2014-09-12 |accessdate=2014-09-14 |archive-date=2014-09-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140913141008/http://www.bbc.com/sport/0/football/29178841 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

===國家隊===
2003年2月12日在[[南安普顿足球俱乐部|修咸頓]]表現出色的比亞堤獲選首次代表[[英格蘭足球代表隊|英格蘭大國腳]]友賽[[澳洲國家足球隊|澳洲]]，澳洲爆冷3-1取勝兼歷來首次擊敗英格蘭<small><ref>{{cite news
|url=http://www.theage.com.au/articles/2003/02/13/1044927700559.html
|title=Socceroos win 3-1 against England
|work=The Age
|date=2003-02-14
|accessdate=2009-01-13
|archive-date=2008-10-31
|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081031133707/http://www.theage.com.au/articles/2003/02/13/1044927700559.html
|dead-url=no
}}</ref></small>。其後再在友賽[[塞爾維亞及黑山國家足球隊|塞黑]]及[[克羅地亞國家足球隊|克羅地亞]]獲後補上場。9月10日再次正選在[[2004年欧洲足球锦标赛|歐國盃外圍賽]]主場出戰[[列支敦士登國家足球隊|列支敦士登]]。11月16日在[[奧脫福球場|奧脫福球場]]友賽[[丹麥國家足球隊|丹麥]]下半場入替[[埃米尔·赫斯基|希斯基]]。

比亞堤沒有入選2004年[[2004年欧洲足球锦标赛|葡萄牙歐國盃]]的英格蘭大軍，當時的領隊[[斯文·約蘭·艾歷臣|艾歷臣]]挑選了入球數目遠低的[[埃米尔·赫斯基|希斯基]]作為「傳統」的中鋒，比亞堤此後再沒有入選國家隊。

== 私人生活 ==
比亞堤在2006年5月在[[曼徹斯特|曼徹斯特]]與未婚妻莎拉·倫德爾（{{lang|en|Sarah Rendle}}）結婚，兩人育有兩子一女。

